<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-center text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Why DAWIN</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black text-center mb-16">ダウインで働く3つの理由</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-1 sm:gap-6 max-w-[200px] sm:max-w-2xl mx-auto">

      <div class="tap-card hex-card group relative overflow-hidden bg-gray-100 cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center aspect-square">
        <div class="w-[58%] relative z-[1] text-center transition-all duration-200 group-hover:opacity-0 group-hover:scale-95">
